                        </a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="cc1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <a target="_blank" href="http://www.gearbest.com/my-orders.html">
                                    Aceder às suas encomendas no Gearbest
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Clicar numa encomenda (Onde diz Order number: ID <- Clicar neste id)
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Escolher a aba "Track You Shippment" e copiar o "Shippment number" &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                <a target="_blank" href="/img/example_gearbest.png">Ver imagem de ajuda</a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <br>
                        <p><strong>Deverá obter o Shippment number, é algo assim: PQ4F6P2342340181150W</strong></p>
